@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_frpqmo(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v0
    tmp = (wp.exp((v1 + 0.46 / v0 + 0.55)) * (wp.sin(tmp + 0.76) * (v0 + 0.26 + v2 + 0.96)))
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.sin(wp.exp(v1 + 0.38)))
    v0 = wp.cos((wp.sin(tmp + 0.33) / (v1 + 0.85 + tmp + 0.65)))
    tmp = 0.50
    v0 = ((0.50 - (v2 + 0.65 / v1 + 0.88)) + wp.exp((tmp + 0.98 / v2 + 0.56)))
    tmp = (v0 * wp.sin(tmp))
    data[tid] = v0
